  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sponsor to Educate &amp; Empower Children in Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">It is estimated that over a million children are out of school in Zambia. Many parent/guardians  fail to take their children to school. We enroll these children from poor  communities and provide them with both primary and junior secondary education. 450 students are currently enrolled with Destiny Community Schools in Matero.  It is our goal for the orphaned and vulnerable children  to be given an education which will empower them to break out of the cycle of poverty.</narrative>
  </description>
